    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Primurudem </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Basilia donat in templum Martis ani<lb break="no" n="2"/>lum <note>sic</note> argenteum si servus si liber <lb n="3"/>m<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>dius</abbr></expan> fuerit vel aliquid de hoc <lb n="4"/>noverit ut <expan><abbr>sanguin</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> et liminibus <note>sic</note> ob <note>sic</note> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> omnibus <note>sic</note> membris <note>sic</note> configatur vel et<lb break="no" n="2"/>iam intestinis excomesis <expan><ex>om</ex><abbr>nibus</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>habe</abbr><ex>at</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>is qui anilum <note>sic</note> involavit <note>sic</note> vel qui medius <lb n="4"/>fuerit
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Material: Blei-Zinn-Kupfer-Legierung. Datierung: nach Hassall - Tomlin ins 4. Jh. aufgrund Schriftbild und Name Basilia. Gebet für Gerechtigkeit. (B): In Z. 3 (ta)mdiu siluerit statt m(e)dius fuerit.</p>
            </div>
